source.oracleReaderQuery:
select
evi.evi_id as eventid
,evi.evi_start_time as eventTimestamp
,evi_created as createdTimestamp
,evi_modified as modifiedTimestamp
,m.m_id as memberid
,cast(cast(spl.spl_abc_id as int) as varchar(6)) as ClubNumber
from betadata.eventitems evi
join betadata.serviceproviderlocations spl on evi.vpd_id=spl.vpd_id and evi.spl_id=spl.spl_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN betadata.EVENTROLLS er ON er.vpd_id = evi.vpd_id AND er.evi_id = evi.evi_id
LEFT OUTER JOIN betadata.MEMBERS m ON m.vpd_id = er.vpd_id AND m.m_id = er.m_id
where TRUNC(evi.evi_start_time) between TRUNC(current_date - 30) and TRUNC(current_date + 61)

select distinct 
	[eventId] ,
	[eventTimestamp],
	[events_createdTimestamp] ,
	[events_modifiedTimestamp],
	[memberId] ,
	evi.[ClubNumber] 
from [Abcpi].[stg_events_deleted_check_incr] evi
join DimFact.DimClub c on evi.clubnumber=c.ClubNumber
WHERE active_ind=1 and sourcenm='ABC';

select distinct 
	[eventId] ,
	[eventTimestamp],
	[events_createdTimestamp] as createdTimestamp,
	[events_modifiedTimestamp] as modifiedTimestamp,
	evi.[ClubNumber] 
from [Abcpi].[stg_events_deleted_check_incr] evi
join DimFact.DimClub c on evi.clubnumber=c.ClubNumber
WHERE active_ind=1 and sourcenm='ABC';
